com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core
Interface ExplicitContract

All Superinterfaces:
Agreement, ConfigurationContract, DeployModelObject
public interface ExplicitContract
extends ConfigurationContract

A representation of the model object 'Explicit Contract'. A configuration contract that exposes user-chosen content as visible and configurable.

The following features are supported:

  • Exported Units
  • Properties
  • Default Conceptual Policy
  • Default Policy

See Also:
